            <lb xml:id="uuid_09999c56-7356-41b2-9f59-0857ec3cbcd4"/><note resp="law-firm" type="paratext"><rs ref="#pmb11988" type="person">Kraus</rs> – <rs ref="#pmb34987" type="institution">Frankfurter städt. Bühnen</rs><lb xml:id="uuid_95a8b4a8-1b56-4ba5-911b-e34b15da85a4"/>expediert 25. Juli 1929</note>
